<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="awesome-adj">awesome <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɔːsəm/    美 /'ɔːsəm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>引起敬畏的；可怕的：</strong></h4>
<p>very impressive or very difﬁcult and perhaps rather frightening：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They had an awesome task ahead.
前面有十分艰巨的任务等着他们。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[尤用于美语，非正式用语] 极好的；了不起的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is only one word to describe the best player in the world — awesome!
只有一个词能够形容这位世界上最好的球员——了不起！</p><footer>人教⑦ – 1</footer></div></div>